way to create an Action

00:00:20.090 --> 00:00:22.640
and to learn more about
the powerful features

00:00:22.640 --> 00:00:25.070
of the Actions on
Google Platform.

00:00:25.070 --> 00:00:27.150
We've added sample
Actions that allow

00:00:27.150 --> 00:00:31.332
you to create working Actions
within just a few minutes.

00:00:31.332 --> 00:00:33.290
You end up with source
code that you can easily

00:00:33.290 --> 00:00:35.760
edit to add new features.

00:00:35.760 --> 00:00:38.570
You can find these new samples
on our developer documentation

00:00:38.570 --> 00:00:40.380
site.

