recording of each Action.

00:01:15.290 --> 00:01:17.760
Once you've selected the
Action you want to create,

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:20.300
click on that type.

00:01:20.300 --> 00:01:22.620
Dialogflow will walk
you through a few steps

00:01:22.620 --> 00:01:27.070
for building an agent that
will implement your Action.

00:01:27.070 --> 00:01:31.080
Firstly, you'll be prompted
to give your new agent a name.

00:01:31.080 --> 00:01:33.120
If you've used
Dialogflow before,

00:01:33.120 --> 00:01:36.560
you can overwrite
an existing agent.

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:38.930
A Dialogflow agent is
created for you, including

00:01:38.930 --> 00:01:42.170
all the intents, entities,
and fulfillment and code

00:01:42.170 --> 00:01:44.330
to make the Action work.

00:01:44.330 --> 00:01:49.330
Within just a few minutes, your
Action will be ready to use.

00:01:49.330 --> 00:01:53.410
Your agent is preconfigured with
intents and working fulfillment

00:01:53.410 --> 00:01:57.510
code that implement
our best practices.

00:01:57.510 --> 00:02:02.150
